    <string name="how_to_use_content">Welcome to hibts! Organize your life intelligently with these simple steps:\n\n1. <b>Add Tasks:</b> Tap the (+) button above the current tasks list. You can set a time and priority. If a task is not completed by end of day, it marks as missed.\n\n2. <b>Habits:</b> Create consistent routines (daily, weekly, or monthly) by tapping the (+) above the habits section. Daily habits reset automatically at midnight.\n\n3. <b>Yearly Goals:</b> Set big dreams in the Goals tab. Break them into actionable steps to see real progress.\n\n4. <b>Smart Date:</b> In the Tasks tab, selecting a date from the strip or calendar will set that date for any new task you add.\n\n5. <b>Custom Themes:</b> Visit Profile > App Theme to change colors. Try \"Cats\" or \"Dogs\" for fun faded background decorations!\n\n6. <b>Notifications &amp; Tones:</b> Set unique sounds for starting a task or reaching an achievement to stay motivated.\n\n7. <b>Manual Order:</b> Long press and drag any task or habit to reorder them exactly how you like.</string>
